DIggs and Brown back by the time the divisional round against the 49ers. On the other hand, the 49ers having a fifth seed would have been worth it. Impressed by 49ers defense defending the goal line on both the seattle catches ...guess they practiced that a lot after the falcons loss....but still, it would give me pause if I were a 49ers fan.
